('cc62cca0-3c26-49db-accb-cc3b7ce7f0b5', '201971ce-3266-4b06-9973-3c753ec502b3', '82b7eba4-446e-4f7a-bdbc-3faa8ec3dec2', 'Faced with this, the individual lets the numbers set the floor and refuses to negotiate against itself, and true to form rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.', 'Slow-walks the decision through every foreseeable consequence before allowing itself to commit. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'Something closer to mild interest than alarm, resolving into relief capitulation — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.73, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
