('71b7db85-46ef-4f85-a899-d1e8f30128d7', '481c3c31-3517-4ca1-b774-036788aa8711', 'e95cf119-80c8-4dcd-b693-25f93b672daf', 'Faced with this, the individual tracks concessions explicitly and matches them one-for-one, never more, and true to form rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.', 'Lays out the options explicitly, assigns each a rough expected value, and picks the one that survives the numbers — distrusting any impulse that cannot be written down. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'The faintest tightening, gone as soon as it is noticed, resolving into euphoric overreach — that resolves almost before it registers.', 0.79, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('150bd75c-dd3b-4d3a-b283-0ffffb2f586d', '7e667c34-7717-48a4-9f2c-942cb907a3f9', '9ea7a7d2-962d-4ed9-a0fe-6e41ea61c5db', 'Faced with this, this profile stays silent past the point of discomfort, letting the other side fill the gap, and true to form holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support.', 'Revisits the same decision from a new angle each time doubt resurfaces, even after nominally deciding. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'A flat, measured pulse with no real spike, resolving into cold calculation — that leaves no discernible trace once the moment passes.', 0.88, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('ad780c13-c3b2-4b72-9e70-b2290ee85c07', 'afe63b9b-7f7f-4bdb-8cfc-dd9f5b558fb8', '424171e3-ca9f-4a67-8171-896465e1dec1', 'Faced with this, this profile holds the line to their BATNA, trading patience for leverage and refusing to move first, and true to form underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.', 'Breaks the decision into weighted criteria before looking at gut feel, and lets the tally overrule any single strong reaction. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'A flat, measured pulse with no real spike, resolving into stoic freeze — that leaves no discernible trace once the moment passes.', 0.93, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('5be55857-3cd6-4603-bd7b-b8fb99bf774e', '929da70c-f375-41fa-afa5-930bbfb1ddee', 'f03c9d14-0322-40a2-9c06-fe0481bc1b70', 'Faced with this, this type holds the line to their BATNA, trading patience for leverage and refusing to move first, and true to form underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.', 'Distrusts the first plausible-sounding answer and keeps testing alternatives until one survives every objection raised against it. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'The faintest tightening, gone as soon as it is noticed, resolving into performative calm — that never really rises to the level of a feeling at all.', 0.89, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('67c7fe40-e46a-455f-b1f2-2fded43ddf9d', '86d3d5a2-21f3-4551-a67f-1fb3ca925fa3', 'b88d5e7f-7f48-4512-ac1c-33baa3cad1ef', 'Faced with this, the individual holds the line to their BATNA, trading patience for leverage and refusing to move first, and true to form prices every token against its all-time high, viewing current levels as an automatic discount.', 'Keeps expanding the list of scenarios to consider until diminishing returns finally force a stop. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'Barely a ripple of concern, resolving into performative calm — that never really rises to the level of a feeling at all.', 0.71, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('5311c9a5-390b-42cd-9cc0-e79266d4d86a', 'cb8701e4-61c6-471d-9bb4-f0e41c7a6253', '2e881f34-77a3-4f9f-87a9-22647da3775b', 'Faced with this, this person stays silent past the point of discomfort, letting the other side fill the gap, and true to form rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.', 'Builds an explicit decision matrix for a call most people would make on instinct, and defers to whichever option scores highest even if it feels wrong. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'Something closer to mild interest than alarm, resolving into relief capitulation — that resolves almost before it registers.', 0.7, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('d3d63e71-4995-4a4e-bc03-03319bd87c04', '03d505bd-d920-4858-af63-38a5c26a685d', '82b7eba4-446e-4f7a-bdbc-3faa8ec3dec2', 'Faced with this, the individual stays silent past the point of discomfort, letting the other side fill the gap, and true to form refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak.', 'Distrusts the first plausible-sounding answer and keeps testing alternatives until one survives every objection raised against it. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'Barely a ripple of concern, resolving into euphoric overreach — that leaves no discernible trace once the moment passes.', 0.75, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('bf8cbdf1-4011-4747-b01b-5b6a12db2441', '0ff3ff93-2a69-449c-908f-c9fafa8fb1d8', 'fc208cd9-cfce-4e79-abb2-61c379d6fc5b', 'Faced with this, this profile lets the numbers set the floor and refuses to negotiate against itself, and true to form is more certain than the hit rate justifies.', 'Lays out the options explicitly, assigns each a rough expected value, and picks the one that survives the numbers — distrusting any impulse that cannot be written down. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'A flat, measured pulse with no real spike, resolving into euphoric overreach — that resolves almost before it registers.', 0.83, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('564ef904-4ea9-4842-8ffd-5c9bc6962eae', 'd383b13f-e716-4ee8-96b9-bc6f270662e5', '60cbb9d1-985b-4442-88f1-f3a01b8b8a81', 'Faced with this, this type holds the line to their BATNA, trading patience for leverage and refusing to move first, and true to form treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery.', 'Treats the choice as a small research problem: gather the knowable facts first, model the downside, then commit only once the math stops moving. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'Barely a ripple of concern, resolving into performative calm — that never really rises to the level of a feeling at all.', 0.76, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('45577d97-0919-4fc5-9ac0-8f9a15359e14', '5a8ce4f5-b569-4927-bcf4-11c71ddd9551', '415b9740-937f-4823-be12-b4507bfa9169', 'Faced with this, this profile stays silent past the point of discomfort, letting the other side fill the gap, and true to form is more certain than the hit rate justifies.', 'Builds an explicit decision matrix for a call most people would make on instinct, and defers to whichever option scores highest even if it feels wrong. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'The faintest tightening, gone as soon as it is noticed, resolving into performative calm — that never really rises to the level of a feeling at all.', 0.87, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('6d079d87-d8da-49c3-b51d-dd6611472d03', '0fbc80be-2c87-4956-804e-c37740b19822', '07157f4f-6707-4e46-84f2-0c61240ba607', 'Faced with this, this profile tracks concessions explicitly and matches them one-for-one, never more, and true to form treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery.', 'Walks every branch and contingency in sequence, uneasy until the residual ambiguity is as small as it can be. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'A quick surge of adrenaline that fades as fast as it came, resolving into fomo buying — that resolves as soon as there is something concrete to act on.', 0.67, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('0945a2b7-5d91-4eb7-92b6-81aec25dd146', 'b499984a-1a8b-48bb-a71e-d77650513470', '5ffd25ad-e2cf-4ead-a2c3-f4d4c93158ee', 'Faced with this, this person lets the numbers set the floor and refuses to negotiate against itself, and true to form measures every later offer against the opening one, not against fair value.', 'Slow-walks the decision through every foreseeable consequence before allowing itself to commit. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'The faintest tightening, gone as soon as it is noticed, resolving into relief capitulation — that leaves no discernible trace once the moment passes.', 0.7, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('6f09f0c3-8b24-4431-9617-75ff0497e0f0', '9f0abea8-7faa-40d5-bcb3-6a42fdeb7b84', 'b766f9b4-2dd2-4224-9863-4fb0c47dc325', 'Faced with this, this person stays silent past the point of discomfort, letting the other side fill the gap, and true to form lets the first number on the table quietly set the whole range.', 'Slow-walks the decision through every foreseeable consequence before allowing itself to commit. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'A flat, measured pulse with no real spike, resolving into stoic freeze — that never really rises to the level of a feeling at all.', 0.7, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
