('f90bbeb8-c73a-4f94-9247-635ce6d3f531', '251ac40b-dc1b-45b2-9193-046a52a6f91e', '58c2d5a2-bc0f-4fc6-b284-6e91527f120b', 'Faced with this, this profile tracks concessions explicitly and matches them one-for-one, never more, and true to form remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along.', 'Builds an explicit decision matrix for a call most people would make on instinct, and defers to whichever option scores highest even if it feels wrong. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'Almost no visible reaction at all, resolving into euphoric overreach — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.72, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('0e1dea09-454f-49b1-b87f-28b2252fb2b3', '634b927e-6599-4a5f-90de-24e552aacc77', '1316d93d-c11e-4497-9b5f-c0573707a20b', 'Faced with this, this person stays silent past the point of discomfort, letting the other side fill the gap, and true to form expects retroactive token rewards for routine protocol usage and reacts with outrage when excluded.', 'Breaks the decision into weighted criteria before looking at gut feel, and lets the tally overrule any single strong reaction. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'Barely a ripple of concern, resolving into cold calculation — that resolves almost before it registers.', 0.7, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('d49f9d40-4db4-4768-b42a-328cdcace046', 'c66f1030-6eff-4e2d-85a7-4bbe9035c285', '9ea7a7d2-962d-4ed9-a0fe-6e41ea61c5db', 'Faced with this, this profile tracks concessions explicitly and matches them one-for-one, never more, and true to form is more certain than the hit rate justifies.', 'Builds an explicit decision matrix for a call most people would make on instinct, and defers to whichever option scores highest even if it feels wrong. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'The faintest tightening, gone as soon as it is noticed, resolving into stoic freeze — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.86, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('ef6b06da-18a1-490b-9cce-b90264c96425', '678e588f-0028-4a6c-b5b8-31ad2a91507a', '9ea7a7d2-962d-4ed9-a0fe-6e41ea61c5db', 'Faced with this, this person stays silent past the point of discomfort, letting the other side fill the gap, and true to form expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately.', 'Builds an explicit decision matrix for a call most people would make on instinct, and defers to whichever option scores highest even if it feels wrong. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'Barely a ripple of concern, resolving into performative calm — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.71, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('fbc89024-5739-4f61-8bee-11e18b0b26e9', 'a397f9e8-0cae-4c4e-a088-902c7fb5215e', '1e29caed-79aa-4aef-b516-376cf6893f62', 'Faced with this, this profile stays silent past the point of discomfort, letting the other side fill the gap, and true to form expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately.', 'Lays out the options explicitly, assigns each a rough expected value, and picks the one that survives the numbers — distrusting any impulse that cannot be written down. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'Almost no visible reaction at all, resolving into relief capitulation — that resolves almost before it registers.', 0.72, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('d5af5238-80aa-4f70-a4ed-9334e07e593f', 'edad9489-9984-449a-b2d1-d806a67f6ddb', 'cfa6ac84-bdab-4496-86fe-23ab7fd040cc', 'Faced with this, this type holds the line to their BATNA, trading patience for leverage and refusing to move first, and true to form assumes the bad statistic applies to other people.', 'Walks every branch and contingency in sequence, uneasy until the residual ambiguity is as small as it can be. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'A flat, measured pulse with no real spike, resolving into relief capitulation — that resolves almost before it registers.', 0.72, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('b9de215e-8b9f-4fbd-ab1a-5c7729fcd11b', '56fdb886-5990-4291-afc9-3c261a3dfb5f', '2694f5ed-254b-4ac0-b2aa-9cce97933cad', 'Faced with this, this person lets the numbers set the floor and refuses to negotiate against itself, and true to form discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 'Builds an explicit decision matrix for a call most people would make on instinct, and defers to whichever option scores highest even if it feels wrong. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'A momentary tightening before the response settles, resolving into fomo buying — that resolves as soon as there is something concrete to act on.', 0.74, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('b6a05ee2-ee9b-43b1-ac73-ca4ffc809d4b', '957bd59c-a0bf-4b96-8043-c8ce32ca5f70', 'fc208cd9-cfce-4e79-abb2-61c379d6fc5b', 'Faced with this, this type tracks concessions explicitly and matches them one-for-one, never more, and true to form prices every token against its all-time high, viewing current levels as an automatic discount.', 'Lays out the options explicitly, assigns each a rough expected value, and picks the one that survives the numbers — distrusting any impulse that cannot be written down. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'Something closer to mild interest than alarm, resolving into performative calm — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.66, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('654dd768-35f2-4c14-8530-79a81efd0537', 'c506bcb1-728c-42a7-a521-5f71895d84f2', '0e8996ad-e932-44ad-84d2-30bcc10990a0', 'Faced with this, this type holds the line to their BATNA, trading patience for leverage and refusing to move first, and true to form rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.', 'Separates the emotional read from the analytical one on purpose, writes both down, and lets the analytical read win the tiebreak. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'Almost no visible reaction at all, resolving into relief capitulation — that never really rises to the level of a feeling at all.', 0.72, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('baac557b-d16b-4df7-88be-04003913695a', '830248ea-6b92-447c-8865-0677a082e31f', 'd650c1d0-9f69-4ce5-957d-21fcabf5d03b', 'Faced with this, the individual holds the line to their BATNA, trading patience for leverage and refusing to move first, and true to form is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling.', 'Lays out the options explicitly, assigns each a rough expected value, and picks the one that survives the numbers — distrusting any impulse that cannot be written down. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'A momentary tightening before the response settles, resolving into defiant doubling — that settles once the choice is made.', 0.69, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
