('0fa19f84-83f6-4cbc-a075-a41ebfb827e0', 'c664488f-b65c-44de-8e26-a72a7bfeaf3a', '2694f5ed-254b-4ac0-b2aa-9cce97933cad', 'Faced with this, this profile protects the relationship, conceding ground to keep the deal and the goodwill intact, and true to form holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support.', 'Revisits the same decision from a new angle each time doubt resurfaces, even after nominally deciding. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'A quick surge of adrenaline that fades as fast as it came, resolving into defiant doubling — that settles once the choice is made.', 0.88, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('5ce0777a-d7ed-4a4e-b02a-fc565babee3e', 'ef1f81ee-786e-4dc3-baab-05eee50d21da', '7b53045a-2a0f-4d68-a017-0b9964c1baaf', 'Faced with this, this profile holds the line to their BATNA, trading patience for leverage and refusing to move first, and true to form never quite escapes the first figure it heard, however arbitrary.', 'Slow-walks the decision through every foreseeable consequence before allowing itself to commit. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'A flat, measured pulse with no real spike, resolving into cold calculation — that never really rises to the level of a feeling at all.', 0.72, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
