('577109ff-1329-4855-9ee3-949a0c54433b', '47d6c334-72dd-4f55-bbef-c30c28fee513', '9c06b3c2-da26-4175-819e-b252688e355c', 'Faced with this, this profile holds the line to their BATNA, trading patience for leverage and refusing to move first, and true to form treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery.', 'Lays out the options explicitly, assigns each a rough expected value, and picks the one that survives the numbers — distrusting any impulse that cannot be written down. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'A flat, measured pulse with no real spike, resolving into performative calm — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.68, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('7df97a49-17f3-4fa6-bc22-43e1fca5fd50', 'cfd25300-b8fc-42b6-9b97-06f5419c704f', '2d6a27cb-94e1-4daa-9ed1-c301d0866c02', 'Faced with this, this profile holds the line to their BATNA, trading patience for leverage and refusing to move first, and true to form holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support.', 'Distrusts the first plausible-sounding answer and keeps testing alternatives until one survives every objection raised against it. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'A flash of heat that cools almost immediately, resolving into appeasement — that resolves as soon as there is something concrete to act on.', 0.83, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('9e6b9b1b-8d46-4a30-a77f-58d55ce263ca', '3ab7921e-c18a-4413-b5f5-659c64a81b0d', '7b53045a-2a0f-4d68-a017-0b9964c1baaf', 'Faced with this, the individual holds the line to their BATNA, trading patience for leverage and refusing to move first, and true to form refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak.', 'Wants the decision to survive hindsight, not just produce a good outcome, so it over-invests in the reasoning itself. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'A flat, measured pulse with no real spike, resolving into performative calm — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.69, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('53c0c1cd-4a4f-45a8-95d0-e052c6d4416b', 'e3df8fd1-5ce4-4b62-afa3-cf3639806a5f', 'b766f9b4-2dd2-4224-9863-4fb0c47dc325', 'Faced with this, this person tracks concessions explicitly and matches them one-for-one, never more, and true to form underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.', 'Slow-walks the decision through every foreseeable consequence before allowing itself to commit. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'The faintest tightening, gone as soon as it is noticed, resolving into performative calm — that never really rises to the level of a feeling at all.', 0.9, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('0facaf77-2534-48e1-be79-76285bd33832', '6f79ffdd-1da5-4df9-b496-962349fa8a49', '19339ab3-2d74-42b1-a905-f84d8a537bcc', 'Faced with this, the individual holds the line to their BATNA, trading patience for leverage and refusing to move first, and true to form discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about.', 'Builds an explicit decision matrix for a call most people would make on instinct, and defers to whichever option scores highest even if it feels wrong. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'Something closer to mild interest than alarm, resolving into relief capitulation — that never really rises to the level of a feeling at all.', 0.74, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('91065052-bee6-4810-8263-82d66ac01abf', 'ba84a735-a3fe-49f2-ab34-62135355681d', 'bbb32ce0-dc71-4d97-b541-d0d38af453db', 'Faced with this, the individual lets the numbers set the floor and refuses to negotiate against itself, and true to form remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along.', 'Separates the emotional read from the analytical one on purpose, writes both down, and lets the analytical read win the tiebreak. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'The faintest tightening, gone as soon as it is noticed, resolving into euphoric overreach — that leaves no discernible trace once the moment passes.', 0.76, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('344d49b2-5ee5-45b7-9048-0078daf2dc39', '364fc065-c61d-4b54-ba9d-f8c5c9b75fde', '70f30104-9656-47f7-a3e3-2c38035c851c', 'Faced with this, this type lets the numbers set the floor and refuses to negotiate against itself, and true to form measures every later offer against the opening one, not against fair value.', 'Revisits the same decision from a new angle each time doubt resurfaces, even after nominally deciding. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'A noticeable but manageable spike of unease, resolving into appeasement — that fades within the hour once the decision is locked in.', 0.67, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('afe9f332-ea31-499d-8bf7-afd0e5517a19', '2a454f23-a15e-4144-92f9-5f5f2778169d', '710fa64f-7abc-4dbf-b354-9ace4f928b54', 'Faced with this, the individual stays silent past the point of discomfort, letting the other side fill the gap, and true to form rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.', 'Distrusts the first plausible-sounding answer and keeps testing alternatives until one survives every objection raised against it. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'A brief flicker of tension, resolving into vindication seeking — that fades within the hour once the decision is locked in.', 0.7, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('702c6d16-ffd8-4e16-bfe7-898ec47c3837', '9f72ceb9-67e9-4d0e-aea0-c687162953f9', 'c7ebfc9f-af74-4032-897d-666eb7715d3d', 'Faced with this, this profile lets the numbers set the floor and refuses to negotiate against itself, and true to form holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support.', 'Lays out the options explicitly, assigns each a rough expected value, and picks the one that survives the numbers — distrusting any impulse that cannot be written down. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'Almost no visible reaction at all, resolving into stoic freeze — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.91, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
('8aa0feab-f2dd-4a89-acb3-1eceb519002f', '4079c713-ec38-4346-8ca5-f42974a2eec6', '9ea7a7d2-962d-4ed9-a0fe-6e41ea61c5db', 'Faced with this, this person lets the numbers set the floor and refuses to negotiate against itself, and true to form expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately.', 'Lays out the options explicitly, assigns each a rough expected value, and picks the one that survives the numbers — distrusting any impulse that cannot be written down. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'Almost no visible reaction at all, resolving into relief capitulation — that resolves almost before it registers.', 0.76, '4556417e-ac86-4549-833b-d3a75bd358ee'),
